column5: I need a 4 piece travel spinning rod. Would like 12-24 line and 9' long , or somewhere in that range. Does anyone know where in Ontario I can buy one of these and have it shipped to me? Thanks
Try Tackle Warehouse, Cabelas or Amazon.
Try Tackle Warehouse, Cabelas or Amazon. Cabelas are a special order at $70 delivery from what I can see. I will try the others. Thanks
